      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA software (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2) operates under ISO 9001-compliant QMS with documented V&V test suite. Required gradation 2: documented software QA plan and regression test evidence available.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 is used under a validated installation with documented QA procedures. Vendor-supplied verification test suite results reviewed and archived. Internal SOP-FEA-001 governs solver version control and installation qualification."
